  "privacyPolicyTitle": "Integritet Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Senast uppdaterad: mars 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your Integritet is paramount. This Integritet Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Datainsamling",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: NNamn E-post address, Telefon number, Datum of birth, and gender. • Hälsa Data: Blood type, aAllergier chronic conditions, mLäkemedel vital signs, symptom logs, and Triage results. • Nödläge Contacts: Names, Telefon numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sSupport • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our Hälsa companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Datalagring och kryptering",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• QR-kod Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. Efterlevnad av GDPR",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tTid • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sInställningar • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can Exportera your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: Alla third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Dina rättigheter",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View Alla your personal and Hälsa data within the app or request a data eExportera • Correction: Redigera your Profil information at any Tid through Redigera PProfil • Deletion: Request account deletion through Inställningar > Data & Integritet > Radera Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any Tid without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app Support feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Kontakt Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns Om this Integritet Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • EE-post privacy@vitalseker.com • SSupport support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to Alla privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
